{"type": "article", "id": 13402, "title": "胶囊旅馆不等于简陋住处，升级版让你喝着咖啡看电视", "description": "这种尺寸极小的旅馆将空间压缩到了极致。", "date": "2015-08-12T13:58:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14235, "name": "胶囊旅馆"}, {"id": 14402, "name": "旅馆设计"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 14403, "name": "空间利用"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 282, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702101641n8CF2t7oUSPaAEjI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t胶囊旅馆（capsule hotels）已在日本流行了不少年头了。这种尺寸极小的旅馆将空间压缩到了极致，据说是为了最大程度上“节省空间、提升效率”。它们花样百出，最近，<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/08/07/business-class-capsule-hotel-in-tokyo/\" target=\"_blank\">东京就出现了一个自称“商务舱”的胶囊酒店</a>，叫作 First Cabin ，和其他胶囊旅馆相比，它的梁顶要高一些，但依旧很窄，设有咖啡吧和屋内电视，墙上还挂有艺术品，重要的是价格依旧很低。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101637WXmdjJKBvqAs6UH3.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"412\" title=\"旅馆全貌\" alt=\"旅馆全貌\" data-ratio=\"0.64375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>旅馆全貌</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101638X2yop89DL0FmEPGd.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"434\" title=\"咖啡吧\" alt=\"咖啡吧\" data-ratio=\"0.678125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>咖啡吧</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101638rO3SHp5AChEiUT6N.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"墙上标有房间号\" alt=\"墙上标有房间号\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>墙上标有房间号</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101638fGq3T5XpdroxFOWh.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"393\" title=\"客人可以在这里喝上一杯\" alt=\"客人可以在这里喝上一杯\" data-ratio=\"0.6140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>客人可以在这里喝上一杯</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101639Ebn4gi9V3R5Fl8Ne.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"412\" title=\"房间确实很窄\" alt=\"房间确实很窄\" data-ratio=\"0.64375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>房间确实很窄</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021016392UQBgu3vSb0Npjsn.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"416\" title=\"first cabin 门口\" alt=\"first cabin 门口\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>first cabin 门口</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101640ZmJv2qn9O7RFV1uy.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"416\" title=\"“海浪”装饰\" alt=\"“海浪”装饰\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>“海浪”装饰</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101640Mcm1xs7fBak3zSZL.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"424\" title=\"每个房间内有平板电视\" alt=\"每个房间内有平板电视\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>每个房间内有平板电视</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em><br>\r\n</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><em><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2015/8/first-cabin-is-a-luxurious-take-on-japanese-capsule-hotels\" target=\"_blank\">hypebeast</a></em> \r\n</p>\n\n"}